there'd be several things we could do.

381
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:44,580
But Kanbara-kun's a half-shade.

382
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:48,810
Frankly speakin', he's such a rare creature that I have no idea how to treat him.

383
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,200
