00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:17,400
I was lost in thought.

392
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,510
It's okay.

393
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,460
That aside, Kanbara-senpai...

394
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:25,970
I'm sure they'd let you stay by his side so long as you ask.

395
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:30,790
