517
00:39:12,970 --> 00:39:15,890
It's probably because of the lull

518
00:39:15,890 --> 00:39:18,130
that your wounds aren't healing at all.

519
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:23,790
They told me you might die
if I attacked you during it, you know?

520
00:39:23,790 --> 00:39:26,150
I was worried about that the whole time.

521
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:32,360
Keep your hands off the wounds!

522
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:34,940
They'll heal once the lull passes.

523
00:39:35,310 --> 00:39:38,830
Don't they say there's no such thing
as good fusion cuisine?

524
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:41,410
